{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e067ba53be","title":"在中央政治局常委扩大会议上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"66cf57a3f3","index":0,"year":1966,"month":4,"day":22,"articleId":"e067ba53be"}],"tags":[{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6f1d1468f8","type":"title","text":"在中央政治局常委扩大会议上的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"e067ba53be"},{"id":"373cced7d7","type":"paragraph","text":"我不相信，在文化革命中的问题只是吴晗问题，后面还要一串串“三家村”。文化革命是触及人们灵魂的革命，是意识形态的斗争，触及的很广泛，涉及面很宽。朝里有人，比如中央宣传都、中央文化部都发生这方面的问题，朝里都有人。各大区、各省市都有。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"e067ba53be"},{"id":"f41589e2af","type":"paragraph","text":"在党中央各部门，包括大区、名省市，朝里是否那么干净？我不相信。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"e067ba53be"}],"page":{"id":"4b59950816","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"e067ba53be","start":496,"end":496}}}},"__N_SSG":true}